Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是她的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界在消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我也会渐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 终于醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡迷糊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次睡眠过后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆都会渐渐变得模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真从容呢 考试考得不错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次因为有长门帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少有点把握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟经常去图书馆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了好处你可要好好谢谢长门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得游乐园不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么地方想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去游乐园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在问长门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你们跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的这里就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是觉得游乐园好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像是第一次来旧书市场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每家店的种类都不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明是文艺社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常好像跟书没什么缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉今天像是在社团活动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 暑假要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说文艺社暑假活动要怎么安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先想想安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚有什么点子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日祭吗 这个不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧 长门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是自己做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门也帮忙了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是帮忙上面衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我品尝一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面衣也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟逛了不少地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 刚才的路还能再走两倍远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我会累垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起图书馆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你还真可能去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 你刚才吃惊了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还真厉害啊 阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟现在的长门相处得跟往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食谱也买到了 满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和文艺社的大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有把朝比奈学姐和鹤屋学姐也请过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想是这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得凉宫马上就会觉得厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是 长门还是觉得两个人比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人独处 和阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 误会什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢他的是之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 身为JK的朝仓 对这个好有兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是JK呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实她的心情 能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是虽说理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在的我和以前的她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解的话 不已经算是恋爱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时一样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是毫无表情地偷看她和他的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感觉能摸到 却又摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 不是我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我将要从这个世界消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在睡觉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会进行身体的调整和记忆的整理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模糊的记忆变得清晰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有根据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但下次睡着 睁开眼睛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我将不再会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何我坚信这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所剩的重要的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 以长门来说还真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐想在外面吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 天气很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什么理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是上次去完古书市场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得喜欢外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是特别的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识一下朝仓真正的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样不告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是一气做得太多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我相信长门一定会说好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算和她说了 结果也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会因此很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 能变回原来的我这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她来说是值得高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 就算说出这种让人不知所措的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她来说也只是增添麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面吃你做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比平时好吃很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超难为情 再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我想笑着告别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 我想看到朋友的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩游戏时候的长门也会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一开始还以为是另外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近和之前的长门越来越像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说记忆恢复的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是因为和我和阿虚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会变成这样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓自我意识过剩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 并不是单纯的治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是恢复到从前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有了他们 我才能成为真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去做晚餐了 待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于读完这本书了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还了这本书之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是说有什么遗憾的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是没能把自己的心意传达给他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 长门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在图书馆借的书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到了该还的日子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经看完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚看完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗是吗 好像是SF吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个怎样的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法直接说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我换个问法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对长门老师来说那书精彩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颇有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颇有意思啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像在看三流恋爱小说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我看了简介之后想看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样 那我决定看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在这能跟你聊天的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门老师推荐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让人失望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别忘了还书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近老跟你去图书馆 去旧书市场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞的我都喜欢上读书了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再去图书馆的话可以叫我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？长门？长门！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然怎么了？长门？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我还不了书了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我还吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 给我等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 你说这个是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别岔开重要的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的告白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要答复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样的答复都是未来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？你现在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这种像以后不会再见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见到我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会变回以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在那之前我一定要传达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 还有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你到达的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个我醒来时肯定会慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能送她到回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感情传达了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就没有什么好留恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 似乎能触碰的到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就该认知到 这一天终会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的长门比以前的长门难聊上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没能发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 怎么说也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我没能注意到也是糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 你给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概会变回以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要说的说完就擅自的消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 你是最棒的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 长门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧？这里是哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚的公园里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这反应 真让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 长门 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 欸？早安？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:10.88,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(994,570)\blur5\fad(695,0)}她的困惑
